    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I know you say it's okay, but it doesn't feel that way. Every time I see them sigh or look at the clock when they're helping me, it just breaks my heart. I've lived my life, I've seen them grow up... and now I'm just the thing standing in the way of them actually living their own lives. It feels so selfish to just keep taking up their time when I don't have much left to give back.",
